Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.73,0:22:53.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.23,0:22:56.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她沒穿我姐這條內褲
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.43,0:22:59.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,洗衣機又啟動了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.59,0:23:04.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她現在沒穿…
